OL,3,CInternational dressage trainer says
OL,4,Cshe 'cannot condone' Dujardin video
OL,6,FAn international dressage trainer and
OL,7,Fformer rider from Gloucestershire says
OL,8,Fshe "absolutely cannot condone" the
OL,9,Fvideo that caused British Olympian
OL,10,FCharlotte Dujardin to pull out of the
OL,11,FParis Olympic Games.
OL,13,FPammy Hutton, fellow of the British
OL,14,FHorse Society, is the principal of
OL,15,FTalland School of Equitation in
OL,16,FCirencester.
