OL,3,CInternational dressage trainer says
OL,4,Cshe 'cannot condone' Dujardin video
OL,6,FShe's a former international dressage
OL,7,Frider, a current dressage rider to
OL,8,FPremier League level, and trains para-
OL,9,Friders, Olympic riders and
OL,10,Finternational dressage athletes.
OL,12,FShe says she's proud to be one of the
OL,13,Ffew horse trainers talking about video
OL,14,Ffootage of Charlotte Dujardin
OL,15,Frepeatedly whipping a horse in
OL,16,Ftraining.
