OL,3,CInternational dressage trainer says
OL,4,Cshe 'cannot condone' Dujardin video
OL,6,FDujardin, 39, has been provisionally
OL,7,Fsuspended by equestrian's governing
OL,8,Fbody, the Federation for Equestrian
OL,9,FSports (FEI), with immediate effect
OL,10,Fafter footage shows her walking
OL,11,Falongside and using a long whip to hit
OL,12,Fthe legs of a horse, that she is
OL,13,Ftraining, more than 20 times.
OL,15,FThe horse, which is being ridden by a
OL,16,Fseparate person, can be seen pacing
OL,17,Fnear to the wall of an indoor
OL,18,Fenclosure and kicking its back legs
OL,19,Fout.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
