OL,3,CInternational dressage trainer says
OL,4,Cshe 'cannot condone' Dujardin video
OL,6,FDujardin has said she is "sincerely
OL,7,Fsorry" for the video.
OL,9,FPammy Hutton says in standing up and
OL,10,Ftalking to the media, she hopes to put
OL,11,Fthe positivity back in horse sports
OL,12,Fand the beauty of the top tests in
OL,13,FParis, ahead of the start of the
OL,14,FOlympics on Friday 26 July.
OL,16,FIn an interview with ITV West Country
OL,17,Fon Wednesday 24 July, she said: "This
OL,18,Fis not about me and talent- it's about
OL,19,Ftraining and what we have seen is not
OL,20,Ftraining. I cannot condone the video.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
