OL,3,CInternational dressage trainer says
OL,4,Cshe 'cannot condone' Dujardin video
OL,6,F"Paramount is the welfare of the
OL,7,Fhorse. If a horse swishes it's tail
OL,8,Fbecause of a fly, then the occasional
OL,9,Flight touch of a whip is alright- but
OL,10,Fwhat we have seen is not training of a
OL,11,Fhorse in anyway whatsoever.
OL,13,F"This video should not be
OL,14,Frepresentative of the industry at all."
OL,16,FDuring the interview, the same style
OL,17,Fof whip being used in the video was
OL,18,Fused correctly by trainers at Talland
OL,19,F- something Pammy wished to highlight.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
