OL,3,CInternational dressage trainer says
OL,4,Cshe 'cannot condone' Dujardin video
OL,6,FShe added: "All of our governing
OL,7,Fbodies have brought in a lot of things
OL,8,Fthis year, having the welfare of the
OL,9,Fhorses paramount. We are moving
OL,10,Fforward, thank goodness, from the last
OL,11,Fcentury.
OL,13,F"I'm going to take it back to the very
OL,14,Fsimplest. I love animals- I even have
OL,15,Fmy dog with me out of camera shot.
OL,16,FHorses visit hospitals now, dogs visit
OL,17,Fhospitals, they're good for mental and
OL,18,Fphysical welfare.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
