OL,3,CInternational dressage trainer says
OL,4,Cshe 'cannot condone' Dujardin video
OL,6,F"In September, we watch the
OL,7,FParalympics. Riding for the disabled
OL,8,Fis one of the biggest things that is
OL,9,Fcovered by riding schools.
OL,11,F"Horses are so good for humans and
OL,12,Fhumans need to be good for horses in
OL,13,Forder to maintain horse sports. You
OL,14,Fonly have to look at a horse in a
OL,15,Ffield to see it doing flying changes,
OL,16,Fpirouettes, trodding across the field
OL,17,Fdoing bussage with it's legs up.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
