OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 2   F439A1729464447
OL,3,CInternational dressage trainer says
OL,4,Cshe 'cannot condone' Dujardin video
OL,6,F"The most important aid with a horse
OL,7,Fshould be what you're thinking and
OL,8,Fyour communication with it in order to
OL,9,Fimprove the peace and harmony and the
OL,10,Fdegree of difficulty required when
OL,11,Fyou're competing at Olympic level.
OL,13,F"I think that we need to remember that
OL,14,Fthe positives outweigh the negatives.
OL,15,FSocial media can be incredibly
OL,16,Fdetrimental.
OL,18,F"Today, I hope to put the positive
OL,19,Fslant back on dressage and the beauty
OL,20,Fof the top tests that we'll see in
OL,21,FParis next week."
